{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b5a5ebd36","title":"中国共产党合肥市委员会关于大搞粮油代用品的指示","origin":"来自网络文章","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19b80e9062","index":0,"year":1960,"month":9,"day":13,"articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f8bde375fa","type":"title","text":"中国共产党合肥市委员会关于大搞粮油代用品的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"dca95601fe","type":"appellation","text":"主送","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"6ddfff4bdf","type":"paragraph","text":"肥东、肥西、巢县县委，巢湖区委，各城乡人民公社党委","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"89e1b1dbbb","type":"appellation","text":"抄送","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"87b32171ac","type":"paragraph","text":"市委各部委，粮食局、商业局党委，存档。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"d62e80437a","type":"paragraph","text":" （共印100份）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"7525d9a00f","type":"appellation","text":"本件    页","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"ce07a514a2","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共合肥市委1960年9月13日印发","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"4d07fbad0c","type":"paragraph","text":"为了认真贯彻中央和省委关于开展群众性增产节约运动，大搞代食品，节约粮食的指示精神，各地应在搞好粮食生产和把粮食收好、管好、用好、安排好人民生活的同时大搞瓜菜，大搞代食品和代用品，节约粮食，增加储备，留有余地。凡是可以腌晒的瓜菜、山芋叶、芝麻叶等要及时晒干储存；凡是可制淀粉的各种粮食作物秸秆和野生作物，特别是山芋藤、山芋根等，应大力组织群众收集，要求年内每人平均收晒干菜100斤，淀粉原料1000斤，由生产队或食堂统一保管加工，有计划的搭配吃用，如有多余，由粮食、商业部门收购，就地加工储存，安排供应，一律不外调。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"27e21b18ac","type":"paragraph","text":"小菜油料和野生油料，目前已陆续成熟，必须抓住时机，开展一次小秋收运动，同时花生、芝麻、黄豆等秸秆，也必须收集榨油，所有粮食收购站、供应点要全面开展收购，也可委托商业部门代购。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"4c0c5b67ca","type":"paragraph","text":"收购任务和价格由粮食、商业部门另行通知。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"d47bcf627c","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共合肥市委会1960年9月12日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"},{"id":"3caf380e03","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：合肥001-01-0147-014","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36"}],"page":{"id":"227fa25986","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"3b5a5ebd36","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}